@startuml
title <font size=12>Admin - Riwayat Transaksi Flow</font>

actor Admin
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "TransaksiController" as Controller
participant "Database" as DB
participant "ActivityLogService" as Log

Admin -> Browser: Akses Riwayat Transaksi
Browser -> Controller: GET /admin/riwayat-transaksi?filters
Controller -> DB: Load transaksi dengan filter tanggal
DB --> Controller: Return data transaksi
Controller --> Browser: Display daftar transaksi

== Edit Transaksi ==
Admin -> Browser: Klik tombol Edit
Browser -> Controller: GET /admin/riwayat-transaksi/{id}/edit
Controller -> DB: Load transaksi + detail items
DB --> Controller: Return transaksi + barang info
Controller --> Browser: Display form edit dengan qty items

Admin -> Browser: Ubah jumlah item dan submit
Browser -> Controller: PUT /admin/riwayat-transaksi/{id}
Controller -> DB: Start Transaction
DB --> Controller: Transaction started

Controller -> DB: Validate stok untuk qty baru
DB --> Controller: Stok check result

Controller -> DB: Update detail_transaksi qty
Controller -> DB: Update stok barang (increment/decrement)
DB --> Controller: Update success

Controller -> DB: Calculate new total
Controller -> DB: Update transaksi total_harga
DB --> Controller: Total updated

Controller -> Log: Log activity perubahan
Log -> DB: Insert activity log
DB --> Log: Activity logged

Controller -> DB: Commit Transaction
DB --> Controller: Transaction committed

Controller --> Browser: Redirect ke riwayat dengan success message
Browser --> Admin: Show update success

== Delete Transaksi ==
Admin -> Browser: Klik tombol Delete
Browser -> Controller: DELETE /admin/riwayat-transaksi/{id}
Controller -> DB: Start Transaction
DB --> Controller: Transaction started

Controller -> DB: Load transaksi + detail items
DB --> Controller: Return transaksi data

Controller -> DB: Get semua detail items
loop Setiap item
  Controller -> DB: Increment stok barang (refund)
  DB --> Controller: Stok updated
end

Controller -> DB: Delete detail_transaksi
Controller -> DB: Delete transaksi
DB --> Controller: Delete success

Controller -> Log: Log activity penghapusan
Log -> DB: Insert delete log
DB --> Log: Activity logged

Controller -> DB: Commit Transaction
DB --> Controller: Transaction committed

Controller --> Browser: Redirect ke riwayat dengan success message
Browser --> Admin: Show delete success

@enduml
